}

(go-to: "World Map")

:: World Map
**THORNWICK REGION - Year $year, $season**

You stand at the crossroads of destiny. Your legend begins here. Where will you venture?

**Status:** Lvl $level | HP: $health/$maxHealth | Gold: $gold gp | Followers: $followerCount
**Stats:** STR $strength | AGI $agility | INT $intelligence | DEF $defense | XP: $experience

---

**Major Locations:**

**→ THORNWICK TOWN** — The starting hub with merchants, quests, and NPCs
[[Visit Thornwick Town]]

**→ BRIGAND CAMP** — Dangerous bandits roam these hills (Combat likely)
[[Travel to Brigand Camp]]

**→ ANCIENT FOREST** — Dark magic and secrets lurk within (Story quest area)
[[Enter Ancient Forest]]

**→ NORTHERN OUTPOST** — Guard garrison and military influence
[[Visit Northern Outpost]]

**→ MERCHANT CARAVAN** — Traveling traders with rare goods
[[Find Merchant Caravan]]

**→ BANDIT HIDEOUT** — A dangerous stronghold (High Risk / High Reward)
[[Raid Bandit Hideout]]

**→ ABANDONED RUINS** — Archaeological treasures and mystery
[[Explore Abandoned Ruins]]

---

**Current Quest:** $mainQuest

**Faction Reputation:**
• Guards: (print: $factionReputation's "Guards")
• Merchants: (print: $factionReputation's "Merchants")
• Bandits: (print: $factionReputation's "Bandits")

**Active Quests:**
{
  (if: $questLog's length > 0)[
    (for: each _q, ...$questLog)[
      • _q
    ]
  ]
}

---

[[Rest and Recover]] | [[Check Inventory]] | [[View Character Sheet]]

:: Rest and Recover
You find a safe place to rest. Time passes as you recover your strength.

(set: $day to $day + 1)
(set: $health to $maxHealth)
(set: $time to "Morning")

(if: $day % 30 is 0)[
  (set: $season to (if: $season is "Spring" then "Summer" else if: $season is "Summer" then "Fall" else if: $season is "Fall" then "Winter" else "Spring"))
  (if: $season is "Spring")[
    (set: $year to $year + 1)
  ]
]

You wake up refreshed. The day is new.

